 <section class="relative text-center text-white py-[120px] px-5 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(15,23,42,.9),rgba(30,41,59,.85)),url(&#39;https://legalx24.com/img/startup.jpg&#39;)] bg-cover bg-center">
      <h1 class="font-black text-[clamp(36px,4vw,50px)] mb-3"> Startup Legal Advisory &amp; Business Structuring </h1>
      <p class="max-w-[950px] mx-auto text-[17.5px] leading-[1.85]"> Starting a business is exciting, but early legal decisions can shape how smoothly your startup grows. The right structure, agreements, and compliance from day one help avoid future disputes and make your venture more attractive to investors. </p></section><section class="py-[60px] px-5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <div class="row items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
               <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(26px,3vw,34px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-[14px] after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[65px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-[#f97316] after:mt-[6px]"> Legal Foundation for Startups </h2>
               <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155] mb-[14px]"> Every startup needs a clear legal base — choosing the right entity, defining ownership, protecting the brand, and planning compliance from the start. These steps may feel small initially but can save major trouble later. </p>
               <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155]"> A properly incorporated and legally structured startup runs more smoothly, handles growth better, and avoids unnecessary founder or regulatory conflicts. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
               <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/startup-1.jpg" class="w-full rounded-[14px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,.2)] transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[6px] hover:shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,.3)]" alt="Startup Legal Consultation" data-themekey="#"/> &#160; </div>
         </div>
      </div> </section><section class="py-[60px] px-5 bg-[#f8fafc]">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(26px,3vw,34px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-[14px] after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[65px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-[#f97316] after:mt-[6px]"> Founders Agreement &amp; Equity Structuring </h2>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155] mb-[14px]"> One of the biggest mistakes early startups make is skipping proper founder documentation. Clearly defining roles, investment, ownership share, decision rights, and exit conditions avoids misunderstandings later. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155]"> A balanced equity structure ensures fairness today while keeping the company flexible for future funding and expansion. </p>
         <div class="bg-white border-l-[6px] border-[#f97316] p-[24px] rounded-[10px] my-[30px] shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,.08)] font-semibold"> Proper agreements at the beginning are far easier — and cheaper — than resolving founder disputes after the business grows. </div>
      </div> </section><section class="py-[60px] px-5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <div class="row items-center">
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-2">
               <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(26px,3vw,34px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-[14px] after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[65px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-[#f97316] after:mt-[6px]"> Investor Documentation &amp; Funding Rounds </h2>
               <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155] mb-[14px]"> When raising funds, investors expect proper documentation — term sheets, shareholder agreements, subscription documents, and regulatory compliance. </p>
               <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155]"> Clean legal records and structured documentation make due diligence easier and significantly improve investor confidence in your startup. </p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 order-lg-1">
               <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/startup-2.jpg" class="w-full rounded-[14px] shadow-[0_18px_40px_rgba(0,0,0,.2)] transition duration-300 hover:-translate-y-[6px] hover:shadow-[0_28px_60px_rgba(0,0,0,.3)]" alt="Startup Funding Legal Discussion" data-themekey="#"/> &#160; </div>
         </div>
      </div> </section><section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0f172a] to-[#1e293b] text-white py-[60px] px-5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(26px,3vw,34px)] mb-[14px]"> Intellectual Property &amp; Risk Protection </h2>
         <p class="leading-[1.9] mb-[14px]"> Your brand name, logo, product idea, software, and confidential data are valuable business assets. Protecting them early through proper registrations and agreements prevents misuse and strengthens your market position. </p>
         <p class="leading-[1.9]"> Simple steps like trademark filing, NDA usage, and IP ownership clarity can save startups from serious disputes later. </p>
      </div> </section><section class="py-[60px] px-5">
      <div class="container mx-auto">
         <h2 class="font-extrabold text-[clamp(26px,3vw,34px)] text-[#0f172a] mb-[14px] after:content-[&#39;&#39;] after:block after:w-[65px] after:h-[3px] after:bg-[#f97316] after:mt-[6px]"> Compliance &amp; Regulatory Advisory </h2>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155] mb-[14px]"> Startups also need to stay on top of routine compliance — company filings, taxation, employment rules, contracts, and sector-specific regulations. </p>
         <p class="text-[16px] leading-[1.9] text-[#334155]"> Regular compliance keeps the business legally secure and builds trust with investors, partners, and customers. </p>
